government of India, because just like there’s

00:14:24.949 --> 00:14:29.259
a federal structure in America, and your taxation
system in Massachusetts is different from

00:14:29.259 --> 00:14:34.411
the taxation system of Oregon, Oregon is different
from the taxation system in New York, they

00:14:34.411 --> 00:14:36.240
made it one uniform GST.

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:41.980
Before that, Bill Gates—and I have a story
in there, how Bill Gates and the other IT

00:14:41.980 --> 00:14:44.540
industry worked to get cash banned.

00:14:44.540 --> 00:14:46.709
They called it the “war on cash.”

00:14:46.709 --> 00:14:49.779
Now, 90 percent of India’s economy is cash.

00:14:49.779 --> 00:14:53.769
Overnight, everyone lost their lifetime savings.

00:14:53.769 --> 00:14:55.350
Everyone was made poor.

00:14:55.350 --> 00:14:57.550
Everyone was made vulnerable.

00:14:57.550 --> 00:15:00.240
Demonetization is what it was called, and
the GST.

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:04.629
These are the two things that are being debated
in our national election lead-up right now.

00:15:04.629 --> 00:15:09.620
Bezos is now working with our dear Bill Gates.

00:15:09.620 --> 00:15:15.529
They want a 0 percent duty—0 percent duty—on
e-commerce.

00:15:15.529 --> 00:15:18.499
Does it mean that when they ship things, they
don’t ship goods?

00:15:18.499 --> 00:15:23.300
No, they ship goods, but with zero taxation.

00:15:23.300 --> 00:15:28.060
The person on the ground in a real local economy
will be paying a tax.

00:15:28.060 --> 00:15:30.339
As it is, they have become more expensive.

00:15:30.339 --> 00:15:34.380
The real economy has been made artificially
more expensive because of the cheating by

00:15:34.380 --> 00:15:35.380
the money machine.

00:15:35.380 --> 00:15:38.519
AMY GOODMAN: How did Bill Gates come to exert
such power?

00:15:38.519 --> 00:15:44.779
VANDANA SHIVA: Well, as is known and is in
the book, Bill Gates did not invent anything.

00:15:44.779 --> 00:15:50.149
The BASIC program was made by some mathematics
professors in a college.

00:15:50.149 --> 00:15:55.579
The Office operating system was by a software
engineer, and he bought it for $50,000.

00:15:55.579 --> 00:16:01.440
He’s built an empire by creating patents
on software.

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:07.740
And the first WTO meeting in Singapore gave
him tax concessions, which is why all the

00:16:07.740 --> 00:16:09.920
IT industry moved to India.

00:16:09.920 --> 00:16:16.089
The fact that Silicon Valley became India
Silicon Valley is because they could save

00:16:16.089 --> 00:16:23.629
$40 billion annually by paying lower wages
for the same work.

00:16:23.629 --> 00:16:27.670
It was an outsourcing of software, all for
Bill Gates.

00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:34.389
With his accumulation of money and making
any communication system illegal, like the

00:16:34.389 --> 00:16:39.770
communication system through real currency
and forcing digital payments, he’s the one

00:16:39.770 --> 00:16:45.089
who gains, because all the software for all
the digital economy, he collects rents and

00:16:45.089 --> 00:16:46.749
royalties on that.

00:16:46.749 --> 00:16:50.410
And then he started to put some of his money
into philanthropy.

00:16:50.410 --> 00:16:51.410
And everyone thinks, “Wow!

00:16:51.410 --> 00:16:52.850
He’s such a generous man.

00:16:52.850 --> 00:16:54.420
He gives so much.”

00:16:54.420 --> 00:16:57.070
But I’ve done an analysis in the book.

00:16:57.070 --> 00:17:00.079
Every place he gives to is his former future
markets.

00:17:00.079 --> 00:17:01.769
I’ll give you a simple example.

00:17:01.769 --> 00:17:08.050
So, the first generation of GMOs, the Bt cotton,
the Roundup Ready soy and Roundup Ready corn,

00:17:08.050 --> 00:17:10.640
have started to breed superpests and superweeds.

00:17:10.640 --> 00:17:17.459
So now they’re trying to get new GMOs based
on gene editing and gene drives.

00:17:17.459 --> 00:17:25.250
In gene editing, not only is Gates financing
the research, he has created a company for

00:17:25.250 --> 00:17:26.250
the patents.

00:17:26.250 --> 00:17:27.740
It’s called Editas.

00:17:27.740 --> 00:17:32.679
So, he will collect rents when gene editing
is pushed through.

00:17:32.679 --> 00:17:38.429
And worse, in the United States, half the
farmlands are overtaken by superweeds.

00:17:38.429 --> 00:17:41.159
The most important one is Palmer amaranth.

00:17:41.159 --> 00:17:42.409
Amaranth is a sacred crop for us.

00:17:42.409 --> 00:17:43.630
We eat it.

00:17:43.630 --> 00:17:50.770
Now, the U.S. Defense system DARPA and Bill
Gates have joined hands for a new technology

00:17:50.770 --> 00:17:54.029
called gene drives to push species to extinction.

00:17:54.029 --> 00:17:56.399
And they want to drive the amaranth to extinction.

00:17:56.399 --> 00:18:00.880
And there’s a footnote in that report saying,
“Oh, yeah, there will be a food insecurity

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:01.960
impact on India.

00:18:01.960 --> 00:18:02.960
They eat amaranth.”

00:18:02.960 --> 00:18:06.409
No, there will be a food security impact on
the world.

00:18:06.409 --> 00:18:11.350
There is an—this is an acceleration of the
race to extinction.

00:18:11.350 --> 00:18:12.480
It is immoral.

00:18:12.480 --> 00:18:13.580
It should be made illegal.

00:18:13.580 --> 00:18:19.360
AMY GOODMAN: A recent report by Oxfam India
reveals billionaire fortunes in India increased

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:23.460
