00:18:33.080 --> 00:18:36.490
half, the world’s poorest 50 percent.

00:18:36.490 --> 00:18:39.140
Economic inequality hits women and girls the
hardest.

00:18:39.140 --> 00:18:44.630
This is Oxfam Executive Director Winnie Byanyima
speaking at the World Economic Forum in Davos

00:18:44.630 --> 00:18:45.630
last month.

00:18:45.630 --> 00:18:52.120
WINNIE BYANYIMA: So, last year alone, we saw
