00:19:00.169 --> 00:19:02.320
by $500 million a day.

00:19:02.320 --> 00:19:09.539
… I’m here in Davos to call on governments
to wake up and take up their responsibility

00:19:09.539 --> 00:19:15.919
and tax fairly, tax wealth and put money in
