00:19:15.919 --> 00:19:18.040
AMY GOODMAN: That’s Oxfam’s executive
director.

00:19:18.040 --> 00:19:19.040
Vandana Shiva?

00:19:19.040 --> 00:19:23.250
VANDANA SHIVA: Yeah, Winnie’s a dear friend,
